55+ aCTIVE LIVING IN BEAUTIFUL LAKELAND, flORIDA!
Holiday Park is a beautiful community  in Lakeland, Florida. Conveniently located between Orlando and Tampa, you will never run out of fun things to do and see. The wide variety of natural, cultural, recreational activities and its inviting climate makes playing golf and sport fishing a joy throughout the year.
Visit nearby attractions such as the Bok Tower Gardens, Walt Disney World, Busch Gardens Tampa, or explore nearby museums. Or you can stay at home and enjoy the community activities and lifestyle, which includes a huge sparkling in-ground heated pool, a beautiful recreation center, library, and so much more!
